t-size: 20px; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Equally, senior citizens, beginners, and individuals with specific medical conditions (such as weaker bone structure), should stick with lower-powered massage guns.</p><p style="font-size: 20px; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></p><p style="font-size: 20px; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></p><p style="font-size: 20px; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></p><p style="font-size: 20px; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></p><p style="font-size: 20px; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></p><p style="font-size: 20px; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></p><p style="font-size: 20px; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></p><p style="font-size: 20px; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></p><p style="font-size: 20px; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></p><p style="font-size: 20px; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></p></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-ke